summary: My reaction to the Aggretsuko Christmas Special trailer
title: My reaction to the Aggretsuko Christmas Special trailer
body:
What’s this? Oh, cool! A little Christmas special to hold over for Season 2. Aw, Retsuko looks adorable, wittle Santa-

….uh….why is he looking like that? W…..what’s wrong? What went wrong? What happened?! Haida, tell us, please!

Why is he drinking like that?! What is he looking at?! What’s going on?! Help! HELP! HEEEEEEEEELP!!!!
